etter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font color=\"#0000cc\" size=\"4\"><font color=\"#000000\">紧张的学习之余，有轻松的音乐陪伴是一件惬意的事情。为音乐选择性价比高的配置，各款不同特色的耳机成为学子们关注的焦点。市面上确实有为数不少的廉价耳机，但是在满意价格的同时不俗的音质表现和佩戴感受也是缺一不可。下面为大家推荐声籁系列耳麦V80，希望为学子们的需要提供一点参考意见。</font></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n<font color=\"#000000\"><img alt=\"追求品质首选声籁V80耳麦全面评测！\" src=\"http://image2.sina.com.cn/IT/h/2007-05-19/0fc9ad849c1bf7a2b05d6d304f7956ca.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /></font><br />\r\n<strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">声籁V80耳麦</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 外观上，V80跟传统的声丽电子耳机差别不大。都是采用黑色头戴带，圆形耳壳设计，滴水型的拉伸调节杆。看来在外观设计成本上的节约都用来提升耳机音质了。</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 黑色沉稳的耳壳，中间镶嵌银白色透音单元，美观大方。闪亮的调节杆连接起个性化不锈钢支架，拉缩舒适自然。</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><img alt=\"追求品质首选声籁V80耳麦全面评测！\" src=\"http://image2.sina.com.cn/IT/h/2007-05-19/bf8c5d42f5525e156d574eddf60c9aec.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" />&nbsp;<img alt=\"追求品质首选声籁V80耳麦全面评测！\" src=\"http://image2.sina.com.cn/IT/h/2007-05-19/79a41c15cc8bbc70839acbcfaae7750a.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /><br />\r\nV80耳麦设计</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 左边蓝黑色的编织导线大约2.5米，导线上配备了高灵敏度的麦克风和独立线控装置。</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><img alt=\"追求品质首选声籁V80耳麦全面评测！\" src=\"http://image2.sina.com.cn/IT/h/2007-05-19/04d87b1c95aa16af8fd93dbf016edfdb.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" />&nbsp;<img alt=\"追求品质首选声籁V80耳麦全面评测！\" src=\"http://image2.sina.com.cn/IT/h/2007-05-19/5905620d7645be5a1a2d064b94c1c940.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /><br />\r\nV80细节、做工</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 细节方面做工毫不粗糙，光滑如新。给人雅致的感觉，又不失时尚。</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 头带上有显眼的声籁英文字样，区别于硕美科品牌同类耳机。</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\"><img alt=\"追求品质首选声籁V80耳麦全面评测！\" src=\"http://image2.sina.com.cn/IT/h/2007-05-19/21bf39f584a2dfe284f154474c45dfb9.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-left: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; border-right: rgb(0,0,0) 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" /><br />\r\n包装背面是声籁V80的具体参数，一目了然。</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">音质表现：</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 700\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 初入耳的时候使人感觉有渐进式好感，慢慢渗透听觉。经过&ldquo;煲机&rdquo;后，音质的优劣表现无遗。解析能力十分不错，最重要的是音色平衡。各种不同类型的歌曲都能很好地演绎，无论是电子舞曲还是柔和的人声都没有难倒V80，是在让人有点意料之外。声音在中高频部门比较明亮，低频不失力度，基本上没有明显的缺点。尤其听流行曲，感觉很耐听。所以是十分适合年轻学子平时听音乐学英语的一款耳麦。</strong></p>','images/201309/thumb_img/4683_thumb_G_1379313763357.jpg','images/201309/goods_img/4683_G_1379313763871.jpg','images/201309/source_img/4683_G_1379313763307.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1379313763','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1379313763','67','','0','0','0','0');
