-stroke-width: 0px\"><font size=\"4\">3.提供多色选择，满足个性需求；</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font size=\"4\">4.细密的皮质耳套，贴耳舒适；</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font size=\"4\">5.可塑性鹅颈短麦，方便调整角度；</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font size=\"4\">6.耳壳处集成音量旋钮，操作简单快速</font></p>','images/201309/thumb_img/4701_thumb_G_1379321786542.jpg','images/201309/goods_img/4701_G_1379321786988.jpg','images/201309/source_img/4701_G_1379321786189.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1379321786','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1397767586','67','','1','0','0','0');
