=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font size=\"4\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; A62的麦克风同样是一大特色。短而精致的柱形硬麦设计，造型犹如微型火炬一般英气勃发。一束光亮沿火炬自下往上延伸，直至点亮顶端，那是来自经过钛合金效果处理的装饰件发出的夺目光泽。</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font size=\"4\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;A62同样注重舒适度的处理，在耳罩头带方面采用高档皮革包裹，柔软性高、通气性好，佩戴非常舒适，还能有效保证低音效果。</font></p>','images/201309/thumb_img/4704_thumb_G_1379382266355.jpg','images/201309/goods_img/4704_G_1379382264900.jpg','images/201309/source_img/4704_G_1379382261524.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1379382260','100','0','1','0','0','0','0','1397767569','67','','1','0','0','0');
INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('4713','853','0','ECS004713','声籁K16耳机','+','153','0','','100','0.000','15.00','15.00','0.00','0','0','1','声籁 耳塞 耳塞式 黑','','<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0); font-size: large; font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px\">声籁K16规格:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">产品特点：<br />\r\n1、外型典雅，电镀合金装饰更显精致。<br />\r\n2、独立线控带麦克风组合，功能齐全。<br />\r\n3、15mm钕铁硼扬声器，声音自然纯净。<br />\r\n4、2M超长导线，满足远距离要求。<br />\r\n产品参数：<br />\r\n1、咪头尺寸： &Oslash;6*5mm<br />\r\n2、灵敏度： -58dB&plusmn;3dB<br />\r\n3、方向性 ：全指向<br />\r\n4、阻抗： &le;2.2K&Omega;<br />\r\n5、喇叭直径： &Oslash;15.0mm<br />\r\n6、阻抗： 32&Omega;<br />\r\n7、频率响应： 20~20kHz<br />\r\n8、输出声压： 102.0dB&plusmn;3dB(1KHz)<br />\r\n9、插头直径： &Oslash;3.5mm(立体声 )<br />\r\n10、线长： 约2.0米<br />\r\n11、净重： 約29g</span></font></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"1\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img.article.pchome.net/00/32/42/65/image006.gif\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">声籁K16是双边入耳式设计，不仅适用于聊天，还能用它来欣赏音乐。耳塞外型典雅稳重，背部点缀亮银色的合金装饰，在外观上显得更加精致，还能降低声音在腔体内的谐振，提高音效表现力。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170); text-decoration: none\" href=\"http://auction1.taobao.com/auction/item_detail-db2-6e312fbe1f5820dd11cf0134aebe6c16.jhtml#\"><font size=\"4\"><img title=\"自由酷话 声籁K16/K26麦克风耳塞上市\" alt=\"自由酷话 声籁K16/K26麦克风耳塞上市\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img2.zol.com.cn/product/21/413/ce0GIWjqhhz1s.gif\" /></font></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px\">耳塞外壳部分经过分子电喷技术处理，触感比较细腻，加上边缘打磨得十分光滑，进入耳道时不会有生硬的感觉。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">这款耳塞采用隐形线麦设计，麦克风的拾音孔就设置在小巧的音量线控上。导线采用日式长短线的方式，佩戴好之后麦克风正好位于头部下方较近的位置，得益于它的高灵敏度，使用的时候并不需要刻意调整位置。</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170); text-decoration: none\" href=\"http://auction1.taobao.com/auction/item_detail-db2-6e312fbe1f5820dd11cf0134aebe6c16.jhtml#\"><font size=\"4\"><img title=\"自由酷话 声籁K16/K26麦克风耳塞上市\" alt=\"自由酷话 声籁K16/K26麦克风耳塞上市\" style=\"border-bottom: black 1px solid; border-left: black 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: none; vertical-align: top; border-top: black 1px solid; border-right: black 1px solid; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"http://img2.zol.com.cn/product/21/414/ceMmOUObsEW02.gif\" /></font></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><font size=\"4\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 通过细密的金属网罩，我们可以隐约看到分布均匀的发音孔。15mm钕铁硼扬声器，配合耳塞背部的长方形透气孔，解析力和平衡力都表现出色。<br />\r\n&nbsp;</span></font><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px\">这款耳塞的音质同样走自然平实的路线，没有做过多的修饰，喜欢个性化音乐的人们可能会觉得不够突出。但是聊天时使用，能够使对方的声音显得更加真实亲切。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/1.4 tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(64,64,64); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">综合来说，声籁K16和K26的语音表现都属于干净清透的类型，加上舒适的佩戴感受，可用来长时间网聊；麦克风的灵敏度较高，语音传输流畅清晰，适合喜欢在网上畅所欲言的人群。</span></p>','images/201309/thumb_img/4713_thumb_G_1379390710755.jpg','images/201309/goods_img/4713_G_1379390710984.jpg','images/201309/source_img/4713_G_1379390710655.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1379390710','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1380166167','67','','0','0','0','0');
