INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('4787','858','0','ECS004787','无线手柄雷柏V10双振动无线游戏手柄pc手柄usb接口10米传输','+','158','85','','100','0.000','0.00','101.00','0.00','0','0','1','其它（Others） 不限 1-99 无线','','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h1 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.67em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 36px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">双震动，无线游戏手柄</h1>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(153,153,153); padding-top: 0px\">雷柏v10是一款无线游戏手柄，摆脱了游戏时的线的束缚，可以自由的在信号范围内进行激战。v10拥有12个按键，内置双震动马达。按键可使用驱动进行自定义，让您游戏得更顺畅。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; margin-top: 50px; width: 750px; zoom: 1; color: rgb(0,0,0)\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 300px; float: left\">\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">人体工学，简洁明快</h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 18px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 300px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 12px; padding-top: 0px\">手柄的机身造型和PS2的标配手柄外形差不多，符合人体工学设计，外形简洁、线条流畅，能够良好的贴合手掌，使用时可以牢固的握在手中，并且有着舒适的手感。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; width: 430px; zoom: 1; float: right\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 430px; float: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: 140px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/249789133/T2ZkauXchbXXXXXXXX_!!249789133.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; margin: 10px 0px; width: 750px; zoom: 1; color: rgb(0,0,0)\">\r\n<div style=\"overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; width: 502px; zoom: 1; float: left\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 502px; float: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: 375px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/249789133/T2CIBJXaNdXXXXXXXX_!!249789133.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 30px 0px 0px; width: 230px; float: right\">\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 230px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">2.4G无线自由</h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 18px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 200px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 12px; padding-top: 0px\">可靠的2.4GHz无线技术，在激烈的游戏战斗中再也不用顾及线缆长度了，摆脱束缚，无拘束遨游于游戏的世界。虽然是无线连接，但是这款手柄在游戏中不会出现延迟或无响应情况，连接稳定，对各种按键动作也都能快速响应，丝毫不会影响到对游戏的操作。（如果周围有其他的无线设备同时使用可能会有干扰哦）</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; width: 750px; zoom: 1; color: rgb(0,0,0)\">\r\n<div style=\"margin-top: 70px; width: 300px; float: left\">\r\n<h2 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 300px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">双震动，模拟实战感</h2>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 18px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; width: 300px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 12px; padding-top: 0px\">模拟真实的游戏场景，在敲打、跌倒、碰撞等虚拟动作中，通过灵敏的双振动马达达到近乎真实的现场感。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; width: 399px; zoom: 1; float: right\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 399px; float: none; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; height: 376px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/249789133/T2f.qDXgxbXXXXXXXX_!!249789133.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; margin: 10px 0px; width: 750px; zoom: 1; color: rgb(0,0,0)\">\r\n<div style=\"overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; width: 502px; zoom: 1; float: left\"><img alt=\"\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; 