-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; visibility: visible; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; visibility: visible; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; visibility: visible\"><img alt=\"无线套装 MK520\" src=\"http://www.logitech.com.cn/assets/32001/4/logitech-wireless-combo-mk520.png\" width=\"455\" height=\"500\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; visibility: visible; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">造型优美的键鼠套装，操控便捷、舒适。<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"掌托\" src=\"http://www.logitech.com.cn/assets/32002/2/wireless-combo-mk520.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"140\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">可靠的无线技术</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">使用罗技先进的 2.4 GHz 连接技术进行无线连接，您再也不必为连线、信号延迟、遗漏和干扰而烦恼。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"电力充足\" src=\"http://www.logitech.com.cn/assets/32002/3/wireless-combo-mk520.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"140\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">电力充足</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">鼠标和键盘高效节能，长久耐用，好像根本不需要使用电池一样。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"打字非常舒适\" src=\"http://www.logitech.com.cn/assets/32002/wireless-combo-mk520.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"139\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">打字非常舒适</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">此款键盘带有柔和的圆边按键，采用全尺寸的键盘布局并附带掌托，让您的双手感觉更加舒适。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; visibility: visible\"><img alt=\"无线套装 MK520\" src=\"http://www.logitech.com.cn/assets/32001/logitech-wireless-combo-mk520.png\" width=\"660\" height=\"306\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">此款键鼠套装使用罗技? 先进的 2.4 GHz 连接技术，电池寿命持久，并采用带有柔和圆边按键的全尺寸键盘，造型优美，操控便捷、准确、舒适。<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"罗技 Unifying 接收器\" src=\"http://www.logitech.com.cn/assets/32002/7/wireless-combo-mk520.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"140\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">罗技? Unifying 接收器</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">无线接收器外型小巧，可始终保留在您的笔记本上，并可同时与键盘和鼠标相连，即使您带着笔记本移动时也无需拔下。此外，您可以用其连接多达六个兼容设备。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"先进的 2.4 GHz 无线技术\" src=\"http://www.logitech.com.cn/assets/32002/8/wireless-combo-mk520.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"140\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">先进的 2.4 GHz 无线技术</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">因此，您可以在更多的地方工作或娱乐 － 比如舒适的沙发 － 长距离的无线连接能力可有效消除延迟、遗漏和干扰，有效使用范围达十米。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><a style=\"color: rgb(51,85,170); text-decoration: none\"><img alt=\"无需担心电池问题\" src=\"http://www.logitech.com.cn/assets/32002/6/wireless-combo-mk520.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"140\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" /></a></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">无需担心电池问题</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">长达三年的键盘电池寿命和一年的鼠标电池寿命从实际上避免了频繁更换电池的麻烦。</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"全尺寸键盘\" src=\"http://www.logitech.com.cn/assets/32002/12/wireless-combo-mk520.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"140\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left-width: 0px\" /></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.33em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; padding-top: 0px\">全尺寸键盘</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.4; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">为您提供了充裕的空间 － 按键布局合理，操作舒适。</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"罗技 Incurve 按键\" src=\"http://www.logitech.com.cn/assets/32002/4/wireless-combo-mk520.p