-top: 0px\">电源管理</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">ACPI高级电源管理</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">硬件监控</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">CPU风扇转速可控，SYSTEM风扇转速监视 CPU温度监视，System温度监视，及各组电压监视</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">板载网卡</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">RTL8111E 千兆</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">板载声卡</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">ALC662 6声道</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">主板规格</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">ATX 210*294 mm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style=\"border-bottom: rgb(221,221,221) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">其他功能</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">Colorful Netlive3.0，PXE&nbsp;</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <div>\r\n    <h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">7X24H全天候拷机</h3>\r\n    </div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">7X24H全天候拷机：我们的每一款产品在出货前都会经过7x24H小时的连续高温55度或零下20度不间断拷机，完全无软硬件方面的问题才出库!</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><img src=\"http://admin.colorful.cn/Common/ShowImages.ashx?id=1305b656919f3dbd4b8cb1d5c08fb6ee3cc7\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">防静电</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">防静电芯片七彩虹战斧系列主板采用高质量防静电IC芯片，具有比传统芯片更好的防静电效果。无论是主板后置面板接口(比如常见的VGA DVI HDMI LAN接口), 还是不起眼的USB连接头，每种设备最少配备2颗防静电芯片，全板高达约20颗防静电芯片。这样的用料可以提供主板更佳的防护，透过这种优质组件的使用，降低计算机常见的静电威胁。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><img src=\"http://admin.colorful.cn/Common/ShowImages.ashx?id=1305615fc06265784be69946a5397c0bc119\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">双通道DDR3</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">支持DDR3规格内存，DDR3相比DDR2拥有更低的功耗，更高的带宽，极限频率可以达到2000MHz甚至更高。双通道内存方案则可以达到32GB/s的理论带宽值，是未来高带宽的最佳选择。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><img src=\"http://admin.colorful.cn/Common/ShowImages.ashx?id=12127dcde5dd22e8404aa84dcdbae6819bb9\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">PCI-E 3.0</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">PCI-E 3.0规范将数据传输率提升到8GHz|8GT/s（最初也预想过10GHz），并保持了对PCI-E 2.x/1.x的向下兼容，继续支持2.5GHz、5GHz信号机制。基于此，PCI-E 3.0架构单信道（x1）单向带宽即可接近1GB/s，十六信道（x16）双向带宽更是可达32GB/s。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><img src=\"http://admin.colorful.cn/Common/ShowImages.ashx?id=1212a37526d48fd6454085d61c93a267c74a\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">防雷技术</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">在板载网卡芯片电路前端增加一颗独立网卡才具有的网络隔离变压芯片，不仅可以增强信号，保证网络顺畅，还能起到过压保护，防雷击的作用。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><img src=\"http://admin.colorful.cn/Common/ShowImages.ashx?id=12125fb6a65ba1584526aa6abd9926b61186\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">FCC铁素体电感</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">军工级铁素体电感七彩虹战斧系列主板整板全部使用铁素体电感, 无论是 CPU供电部分还是内存供电部分，与一般电感相比,铁素体电感有突出优点: ●更高的电子阻抗、更低的工作温度、更低的EMI电磁干扰、寿命超长 ●一体成型结构可避免发生噪音 ●同尺寸直流阻抗最低 ●可确保耐电流电感值降幅平顺 ●应用频率可达5MHz ●适用于回流焊SMT工艺 ●产品无铅,符合RoHS指令</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><img src=\"http://admin.colorful.cn/Common/ShowImages.ashx?id=1305876c0f258b54495091e57de7f8035739\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">睿频技术</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">英特尔睿频加速技术是英特尔酷睿 i7/i5 处理器的独有特性，也是英特尔新宣布的一项技术。这项技术可以理解为自动超频。当开启睿频加速之后，CPU会根据当前的任务量自动调整CPU主频，从而重任务时发挥最大的性能，轻任务时发挥最大节能优势。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><img src=\"http://admin.colorful.cn/Common/ShowImages.ashx?id=1212d398d010433647b5a94ff797219446dd\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">USB3.0 接口</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">USB3.0理论上提供了高达5.0Gbps数据传输速率，支持热插拔，向下兼容USB 2.0标准，方便连接各种USB接口设备。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><img src=\"http://admin.colorful.cn/Common/ShowImages.ashx?id=1212ca998536f7ac44539f446d22bd7f924a\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">全固态电容</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">全固态电容指整板全部使用固态电容. 全固态电容具备环保、低阻抗、高低温稳定、耐高纹波及高信赖度等优越特性，是目前电解电容产品中最高阶的产品。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><img src=\"http://admin.colorful.cn/Common/ShowImages.ashx?id=1212ef4fd2019efb4c418b43886d6f382a94\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">千兆以太网</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">千兆以太网络提供更稳定、更快速的网络传输环境，高达1000Mbps的传输速率更好的满足了高数据吞吐量的应用需求。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><img src=\"http://admin.colorful.cn/Common/ShowImages.ashx?id=121240727c473aec46148f8607ae17dc5773\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">三年全免质保</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">七彩虹科技有限公司对七彩虹主板产品实行三年全免费保修服务保证，全国联保。详情请参看保修卡或公布保修条例。</li>\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\"><img src=\"http://admin.colorful.cn/Common/ShowImages.ashx?id=121253aeb1cd33504d4f8f7e5fe81bf8acd6\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px\" alt=\"\" /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-size: 1.17em; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 0px\">智能还原</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: none; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px; padding-left: 40px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\">\r\n    <li style=\"list-style-position: outside; padding-bottom: 0px; list-style-type: disc; margin: 0px; padding-